#define WrestleWin ["Bite me, frag-head! That was barely a warm-up.","You’re lucky I don't feel like splattering you all over the scenery today, %s.","Is that all ya got? I’ve seen space-slugs with more fight in 'em.","Go home and cry to your mama, %s. I got a contract to finish.","You're lucky I'm in a good mood. Normally, you'd be a smear on my boot.","Don't take it personal, %s. Ya just got in the way of a professional.","Better luck next time, pal. Maybe try pickin' a fight with someone less awesome.","You put up a cute show, %s, but you're just another job well done.","Keep scratchin', %s. Maybe one day you'll actually make me notice.","Ya got gumption, I'll give ya that. But gumption don't stop the Main Man.","Whoa! You actually made me bleed a little! Now you're really gonna get it!","You're gettin' better, %s. Keep practice-shootin' and maybe you'll be a threat.","That was a solid hit, %s! Nearly knocked the cigar right outta my mouth!","Ya survived longer than most, %s. Respect for keepin' the fight interesting.","Nice scrap, %s! Don't go thinkin' you're on my level though.","Hey, you ain't half bad, %s. Almost felt like a real tussle!","You're holdin' your own, %s. Not many folks can say that without lookin' like hamburger.","You've got some real moves, %s. Where'd you learn to be such a nuisance?","Respect, %s. You gave me a run for my money. Now hand over the bounty!","You're tough, %s, but I've been kickin' tail since before you were born.","Wow! You really pushed me there, %s. That was a great scrap!","You’ve got a real punch on ya, %s. I’m actually feelin' that one!","I haven't had a fight like that in a while, %s. You're top-notch trash, pal.","You really know how to handle yourself, %s. I’m actually impressed!","You're a powerhouse, %s! Keep showin' everyone how it's done—before I scrap ya.","Now that’s a fight! You're every bit as tough as they say, %s. Let's make it messy!","You almost had me, %s! My hide is gonna feel that one tomorrow.","You're a real heavy hitter, %s. I actually had to step it up! Woo!","I respect ya, %s. You're one of the few who can actually make it fun.","That was some serious scrap, %s! We should do this again when I’m not tryin' to collect a bounty!","Holy frag! You're a force of nature, %s. That was the best scrap of the century!","You’re a true legend, %s. It was an honor to go toe-to-toe with ya, Main Man to Main Man.","You pushed me to my limits, %s. That's a rare treat—usually I'm the one doin' the pushin'!","You’re elite, %s. Let's team up next time instead of knockin' each other around!","You've got grit, heart, and power—you’re the real deal, %s. You're almost worth the bounty!"]

